#~ msgid ""
#~ "Enhance elegance and comfort with our thoughtfully crafted pieces that "
#~ "bring out the best version of you, every day."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Esalta l'eleganza e il comfort con i nostri pezzi realizzati con cura, "
#~ "che fanno emergere la versione migliore di te, ogni giorno."

#~ msgid "Every style for everybody."
#~ msgstr "Tutti gli stili."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Experience perfectly fitted clothing with our bespoke tailoring service, "
#~ "designed to match your unique style and body shape."
